Welcome
About Us
ABOUT US
We’re bringing Southern Hospitality to Dunedin!
Prohibition Dunedin is a Southern Comfort Gastropub (with a twist) bringing you BBQ-inspired dishes, handcrafted cocktails, 37 Taps, and an in-house bakery! We are passionate about bringing a fresh, creative, and unique dining experience to you, your family, and your friends. Experience our welcoming atmosphere inside our local artist-inspired indoor seating or on our spacious dog-friendly, smoke-free patio. The choice is yours.
We’ll see you soon at Prohibition Dunedin.
